#User stories

* As an administrator, I want to create an exam for a course, so that participants can take the exam.

* As a participant, I want to see how many questions that are completed and how many that are left, so that I can keep track of my progress during the exam.

* As an administrator, I want to save an exam as a template, so that the exam can be reused later.

* As a participant, I want to upload personal info, like my name, phone number and a picture, so that it is easier to be identified.

* As a participant, I want to download my certificates, so that I can show them to employers when searching for jobs.
